{"componentChunkName":"component---theme-src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/custom-pages","webpackCompilationHash":"d8e72fdba038183d0b0b","result":{"data":{"post":{"headings":[{"depth":2},{"depth":3},{"depth":3}],"frontmatter":{"title":"Creating custom pages","path":"/custom-pages","tags":["Programming"],"excerpt":"Creating custom pages is easy in Nehalem - let's take a brief look.","created":"2019-07-23T00:00:00.000Z","createdPretty":"23 July, 2019","updated":"2019-07-23T00:00:00.000Z","updatedPretty":"23 July, 2019","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.499867479459316,"src":"/gatsby-blog/static/f942cc0ae9bb12a1329c617c6ef17079/57238/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/gatsby-blog/static/f942cc0ae9bb12a1329c617c6ef17079/5398f/cover.jpg 200w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/f942cc0ae9bb12a1329c617c6ef17079/26a4d/cover.jpg 400w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/f942cc0ae9bb12a1329c617c6ef17079/57238/cover.jpg 800w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/f942cc0ae9bb12a1329c617c6ef17079/23dde/cover.jpg 1200w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/f942cc0ae9bb12a1329c617c6ef17079/526a4/cover.jpg 1600w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/f942cc0ae9bb12a1329c617c6ef17079/96acd/cover.jpg 5659w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"html":"<p>In case you want to create your own custom pages Nehalem provides a bunch of useful tools to make this easier for you.</p>\n<h2 id=\"basic-structure\"><a href=\"#basic-structure\" aria-label=\"basic structure permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic structure</h2>\n<p>The basic structure for pages is:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>FunctionComponent<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Layout <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/layout\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SEO</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/seo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Container <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/common\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> CustomPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> FunctionComponent<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> location<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Location <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>location<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Layout bigHeader<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">SEO</span>\n      location<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>location<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Page title</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Container<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      Your content    \n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Container<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Layout<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> CustomPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Layout /&gt;</code> component either shows a big header (like the one on the front page) or a small one (like on every other page) based on the\n<code class=\"language-text\">bigHeader</code> prop.</p>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;SEO /&gt;</code> component takes care of optimizing everything in terms of SEO. The <code class=\"language-text\">location</code> prop comes from Gatsby.</p>\n<h3 id=\"using-custom-props\"><a href=\"#using-custom-props\" aria-label=\"using custom props permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Using custom props</h3>\n<p>Components often have some props. The <code class=\"language-text\">FunctionDecorator</code> interface allows creating fully typed components like this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>FunctionComponent<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Layout <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/layout\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SEO</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/seo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Container <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/common\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CustomPageProps</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></span>  location<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Location<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  showConditionalText<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> CustomPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> FunctionComponent<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>CustomPageProps<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>showConditionalText<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> location<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span></span>  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Layout bigHeader<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">SEO</span>\n      location<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>location<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Page title</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Container<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      Your content\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>showConditionalText <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>This text <span class=\"token keyword\">is</span> only shown when showConditionalText <span class=\"token keyword\">is</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Container<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Layout<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> CustomPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"the-subheader-component\"><a href=\"#the-subheader-component\" aria-label=\"the subheader component permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Subheader component</h3>\n<p>Some components, like the <code class=\"language-text\">PageTemplate</code> use a small component for a stylish subheader:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>FunctionComponent<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Layout <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/layout\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SEO</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/seo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Container <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/common\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Subheader <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem/src/components/subheader\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> CustomPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> FunctionComponent<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> location<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Location <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>location<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Layout bigHeader<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">SEO</span>\n      location<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>location<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Page title</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Subheader title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Page title</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> subtitle<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Something else</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span>    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Container<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      Your content    \n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Container<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Layout<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> CustomPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<p><em>Cover by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@christopher__burns\">@christopher_burns</a></em></p>"},"primaryTag":{"name":"Programming","color":"#007acc"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"postId":"cde0fecc-15fe-5ad9-8ac0-beb31348aeff","primaryTag":"Programming"}}}